name: Go Go Googles!
description:
Help the goofy jumping Googles in this action game from Webkinz World™!
The more Gozies you grab in a single jump, the more points you earn. Jump into Buzzerflies to keep them from touching the Gozium Bramble. Spell GOOGLES by collecting Goo-Goo Berries, and earn a bonus. It’s time to Go-Go Googles!

* Tilt your device to move Giggle and Gaggle. Tap on them to swap them, to use their different features.
* Tap the screen to jump. At the right time, tap the screen again for an extra boost.

Earn Kinzcash™ while you play! Store and send KinzCash earnings to your active Webkinz World account whenever you have an internet connection. Now you can earn KinzCash while you're on a vacation, in the car, or just hanging out in the backyard.
